description:
The Complete Clive Barker's The Great and Secret Show

Collected here in one deluxe edition is the complete 12-part saga that comprises the comic book adaptation of master of horror Clive Barker's epic journey into the fantastic, The Great and Secret Show (Everville, bk1). Adapted by Chris Ryall and artist Gabriel Rodriguez, this collection presents the ultimate battle between good and evil that spans many decades and dimensions.

Also featuring complete art galleries by Gabriel Rodriguez and Clive Barker, full issue-by-issue annotations by Ryall and Rodriguez, and more!
name: TPB

volume.name: The Complete Great and Secret Show

description: The quest for the Art ends here! Clive Barker's epic journey into the fantastic, The Great and Secret Show, spans decades and dimensions, and it all comes to an explosive finale in this second volume. As the boundary between the Cosm and Quiddity is breached, all the resulting deaths, resurrections, and transfigurations lead our work closer and closer to Armageddon! This collection of the final six issues of the landmark series are once again adapted by the Beowulf team of Chris Ryall, Gabriel Rodriguez, and Jay Fotos. Volume 2 includes a cover gallery with images from both Rodriguez and Barker himself.
name: Volume 2
